snippet: All 13 people aboard a New Zealand skydiving plane whose engine apparently failed Wednesday managed to leap out in parachutes moments before the plane plunged into a lake, the authorities said.
lead_paragraph: All 13 people aboard a New Zealand skydiving plane whose engine apparently failed Wednesday managed to leap out in parachutes moments before the plane plunged into a lake, the authorities said.

headline.main: New Zealand: All Plunge to Safety as Skydiving Plane’s Engine Quits
headline.print_headline: New Zealand: All Plunge to Safety As Skydiving Plane’s Engine Quits
